    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ># 1</h2><strong>一个全新的操作模式。</strong>玩家通过变换指令矩阵（画面右上角）来间接控制角色的行动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376760/extras/c295c5d5f45a1de466aa3f1cb305f417.poster.avif?t=1685059325\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376760/extras/c295c5d5f45a1de466aa3f1cb305f417.webm?t=1685059325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376760/extras/c295c5d5f45a1de466aa3f1cb305f417.mp4?t=1685059325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ># N</h2><strong>数十种指令与机制。</strong>随着流程的推进，会不断解锁新的指令与机制。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376760/extras/891c1e755a87d0a3b244f88037a3b345.avif?t=1685059325\" width=604 height=340 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ># ∞</h2><strong>无限的可能性。</strong>玩家可以自由编辑指令矩阵来实现无数种过关的方式。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376760/extras/c2c2ff454aca02385ef5bd24759fc2e3.poster.avif?t=1685059325\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376760/extras/c2c2ff454aca02385ef5bd24759fc2e3.webm?t=1685059325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376760/extras/c2c2ff454aca02385ef5bd24759fc2e3.mp4?t=1685059325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
